## Project Review Patterns to Honor

These patterns are the catalog the project's review/audit/elaborate tools share — including any project-specific patterns shipped under `.planwerk/review_patterns/` in this repository. Treat them as binding constraints on the implementation: every commit you push MUST stay consistent with them. When the change touches an area covered by a pattern, prefer the resolution the pattern endorses.

<review-patterns>
<technology-patterns>
### Pattern: Missing context.Context parameter
- Category: technology
- Area: reliability
- Detection: long-running Go functions without ctx
- Severity: WARNING
## Rule
Long-running functions MUST accept a context.Context.

</technology-patterns>

<design-patterns>
### Pattern: Hardcoded secrets
- Category: design-principle
- Area: security
- Detection: literal API keys or passwords in source
- Severity: CRITICAL
- Sources: OWASP ASVS
## Rule
Secrets MUST be loaded from environment variables or a secret manager.

</design-patterns>

</review-patterns>

